0.001003 2026-07-16
    - Support single HTTP byte ranges with native reads and compatibility fallback.
    - Add optional storage and blob-store range-read contracts.
    - Close stream bodies discarded after metadata-only reads.

0.001002 2026-07-13
    - Add public metadata-store and blob-store component contracts for storage
      backends that keep metadata and blob bytes separately.

0.001001 2026-07-13
    - Use Class::Tiny for all object construction.
    - Ensure coverage tests load the working-tree modules.
    - Link the top-level server POD to Net::Blossom, backend discovery, and
      the storage contract.

0.001000 2026-07-09
    - Initial CPAN release.
